(42, 2, 18, 23, 8, 18, 18, NULL, 'Connection of Signs and Wonders', 'This connection highlights the theme of ''wonders'' in both passages. In Luke, the shepherds'' message evokes wonder, while Isaiah speaks of signs and wonders associated with God''s children.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
